The Tilde Terminal Toolkit (T3) is a set of libraries for creating terminal
programs. It was originally created for the Tilde terminal text editor as a
replacement for the curses library. However, these libraries can also be used
to create other terminal-based programs. The toolkit consists of the following
libraries:

libt3window: provides overlapping text windows in much the same way as the
  X window system provides overlapping
libt3key:
